                <p>Soil Rigs Private Limited is the leading manufacturer and exporter of Pneumatic and Hydraulic Drill Rigs and related products. Then with a sprit of management philosophy-high quality products, satisfactory services and customer satisfaction Soil Rigs were in pursuit of excellent performance.</p>
                <p>Soil Rig's present directors are Mr. C. DINESHKUMAR, and has the Registered office in Thiruchengode.</p>
                <p>Soil Rigs has the sophisticated manufacturing facilities with highly skilled workers backed by latest technologies and stringent Quality Control Systems. Major export destinations have been African Countries.</p>
                <p>Our Company has been on an exclusive rate contract with reputed organizations for many years for the supply of our products and its spare parts.</p>
                <p>Soil Rigs is the largest manufacuturer and exporter of pumps, borewell rig mounted vehicles, support vehicles, PVC pipes, and drilling accessories.</p>
                <p>Soil Rigs also manufactures and enjoys a significant market share in UPVC Pipes. Along with Rigid PVC items, The company also manufactures UPVC casing pipes, UPVC Scree Pipes, and Suction Hose Pipes.</p>
                <p>As a validation of our excellent quality and our exceptional services, the company has recieved several awards from many different agencies.</p>
                <p>We have experienced significant growth and improvement over the past years, which clearly demonstrates our commitment to excellence. </p>
                <p>The superior product quality and customer support Soil Rigs enjoyed a rapid growth in the local market and upgraded its product line with Hydraulic drilling rigs to cover the world market.</p>
                <p>To better understand our customer needs and to closely monitor market trends, Soil Rigs aggressively participates in major shows in India and abroad.</p>
                <p>With the increase in demand for Soil Rigs rigs in the international market, the trend on quality demands has shifted from Quality Control to Quality Assurance. Our goal is to provide our customer with a superb quality assurance and real value for money.</p>
